## Usage

Define PAAS namespaces and the groups that can manage the resources:

```
namespaces:
- name: test
  serviceAccount: test-account
  account: test
  groups: ['testgroup']
- name: foo
  serviceAccount: foo-account
  account: foo
  groups: ['bar']
```

